HEADWORD: Diarrhœa
<hw>Di`ar*rh⟦oe⟧"a</hw> }</mhw>,
<pr>(d⟦imac⟧`⟦ait⟧r*r⟦emac⟧"⟦adot⟧)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
